  <p class="full-width medium-italic">
    Ol√° Onda Guesthouse has 5 rooms for 2 to 3 people. All rooms have a private bathroom with a roomy rainshower. All beds are made by ourselves, with wood from the Portuguese countryside. Big, sturdy &amp; comfortable were the keywords in building them.
